OL,3,CMurder investigation after boy, 12,
OL,4,C'hit by vehicle' near Brentwood
OL,6,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation after a boy, aged 12,
OL,8,Fwas reportedly hit by a vehicle near
OL,9,FBrentwood in Essex.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to Ashwells Road
OL,12,Fin Pilgrims Hatch on Sunday afternoon
OL,13,Fand found the child with serious
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FA boy aged 15 and a man aged 43 have
OL,17,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,19,FThe victim was taken to hospital where
OL,20,Fhe later died.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
