OL,3,CMurder investigation after boy, 12,
OL,4,C'hit by vehicle' near Brentwood
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,7,FMetcalfe from Essex Police said: "Our
OL,8,Ffirst thoughts are of course with the
OL,9,Ffamily of the boy who has tragically
OL,10,Fdied after this incident.
OL,12,F"By its very nature, this is an
OL,13,Fevolving investigation which has a
OL,14,Fnumber of complexities and will take
OL,15,Fsome time to work through and cannot
OL,16,Fbe rushed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781021473
OL,3,CMurder investigation after boy, 12,
OL,4,C'hit by vehicle' near Brentwood
OL,6,F"We're working hard to build a full
OL,7,Fpicture of the circumstances around
OL,8,Fit, and I'd like to thank those who
OL,9,Fhave already come forward to provide
OL,10,Ftheir accounts of what happened.
OL,12,F"To residents who we have not yet
OL,13,Fspoken to, I would urge you to please
OL,14,Freview any CCTV you have from 8am on
OL,15,FSunday 7 June right through to 7pm and
OL,16,Fplease get in touch through our
OL,17,Fdedicated public portal which has been
OL,18,Fset up for this incident.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781021473
OL,3,CMurder investigation after boy, 12,
OL,4,C'hit by vehicle' near Brentwood
OL,6,F"Although we remain in the early
OL,7,Fstages of this investigation, we are
OL,8,Fconfident this was an isolated
OL,9,Fincident and there is no ongoing risk
OL,10,Fto the community."
OL,12,FChief Inspector Terry Fisher,
OL,13,FBrentwood district commander, added:
OL,14,F"I'm acutely aware that this incident
OL,15,Fis likely to have a significant impact
OL,16,Fin our community, and I know the
OL,17,Finvestigation team is doing everything
OL,18,Fpossible to fully understand the
OL,19,Fcircumstances and progress this
OL,20,Fappropriately.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
